name: TwilioQuest Workshop
description: This workshop will be a 3 day workshop in which we’ll gather our college mates from each year and will acknowledge then with the TwilioQuest.During the workshop we’ll make them complete one track of their choice and will help them understanding the concepts of each track.
applicationPeriod: This workshop will be hosted from 15th of September till 17th of September in our own campus.
